# m3_plasma_smg.shot — Scout with Plasma SMG at moderate range. Verifies
#   - Projectile pool spawn on every fire tick (60 ms cycle)
#   - Hit detection on bone segments (not via hitscan)
#   - Self-bink kicks in over sustained fire (crosshair widens)
# The dummy at 80 dmg/limb takes ~8 hits per limb at 10 dmg each.

window 1280 720
seed   2 2
out    build/shots/m3_plasma_smg
loadout Scout "Plasma SMG" - Light Standard
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

spawn_at 2240 984
mouse    1100 360

at  20 shot t020_idle
at  30 press fire
burst fire from 60 to 240 every 20
at 260 release fire

at 280 shot t280_settled
at 310 end
